Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.util.iteration

Class SizedIterableImpl<T>

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.util.iteration.SizedIterableImpl<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements held by this iterable.
All Implemented Interfaces:
SizedIterable<T>, Iterable<T>
public class SizedIterableImpl<T> extends Object implements SizedIterable<T>
Implementation of the SizedIterable interface. This class provides an implementation for a sized iterable, which wraps a given Iterable or Collection, allowing efficient size retrieval and iteration over the contained elements.
